text: 醬 may refer to: * Jiàng (/), Chinese sauces and pastes ** dòubànjiàng (bean paste) ** hǎixiānjiàng (hoisin sauce) ** jiàngyóu (soy sauce) ** tiánmiànjiàng (sweet bean sauce) * Jang (/), Korean sauces and pastes ** ganjang (soy sauce) and guk-ganjang (soup soy sauce) ** doenjang (soybean paste) ** gochujang (red chili paste) * Shō (/) or ''''' (/), Japanese sauces and pastes ** shōyu (soy sauce)
title: 醬
